    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件令人震惊，世界呼吁结束两极分化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/shock-at-trump-shooting-prompts-world-calls-to-end-polarization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[除了对刺杀唐纳德·特朗普的事件表示震惊和愤怒之外，世界各国领导人在众多声明中还传达了另一个信息：必须做出改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/shock-at-trump-shooting-prompts-world-calls-to-end-polarization</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 11:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑切斯为埃斯克里瓦担任西班牙央行行长的资格辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/sanchez-defends-escriva-s-credentials-for-spain-s-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯极力捍卫数字化转型部长何塞·路易斯·埃斯克里瓦的经济资质，不过他并未支持他担任该国下一任央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/sanchez-defends-escriva-s-credentials-for-spain-s-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 11:32:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫称北约峰会结果对俄罗斯构成“威胁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/kremlin-says-nato-summit-outcome-is-threatening-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫表示，上周北约峰会的结果对俄罗斯来说“具有威胁性”，表明没有理由启动结束乌克兰战争的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/kremlin-says-nato-summit-outcome-is-threatening-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 10:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜王储被任命为阿联酋国防部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/dubai-crown-prince-named-uae-minister-of-defense-in-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国副总统兼迪拜酋长谢赫穆罕默德·本·拉希德宣布，根据政府改组计划，他的儿子被任命为该国副总理兼国防部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/dubai-crown-prince-named-uae-minister-of-defense-in-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 09:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击案枪手是 20 岁的宾夕法尼亚州男子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/suspected-gunman-in-trump-attack-is-20-year-old-pennsylvania-man</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局已确认，周六在宾夕法尼亚州集会上向前总统唐纳德·特朗普开枪的枪手是 20 岁的托马斯·马修·克鲁克斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/suspected-gunman-in-trump-attack-is-20-year-old-pennsylvania-man</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 08:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯否认退出加沙停火谈判的报道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/hamas-is-withdrawing-from-gaza-cease-fire-talks-afp-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在前一天，以色列空袭加沙，造成至少 90 人死亡，300 人受伤，哈马斯否认退出停火谈判。以色列空袭旨在杀死两名哈马斯高级官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/hamas-is-withdrawing-from-gaza-cease-fire-talks-afp-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 08:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Haven Rush，枪击事件后投资者对“特朗普交易”的看法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/haven-rush-trump-trades-on-investor-minds-after-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场观察人士表示，投资者最初会青睐传统的避险资产，并可能倾向于选择与前总统唐纳德·特朗普在躲过暗杀后入主白宫的可能性最相关的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/haven-rush-trump-trades-on-investor-minds-after-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 03:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普遇刺受伤 各国领导人作出反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/world-leaders-react-after-trump-injured-in-shooting-at-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，前总统唐纳德·特朗普在集会上遭枪击受伤，至少一名参加者死亡，世界各国领导人谴责政治暴力，并祝愿特朗普早日康复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/world-leaders-react-after-trump-injured-in-shooting-at-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:41:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普遭暗杀后“罚款”，FBI 公布嫌疑人名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/trump-rushed-off-stage-at-pennsylvania-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，周六宾夕法尼亚州一场集会上突然爆发枪击，他的右耳中弹，这一令人痛心的事件震惊了美国总统竞选，并引起两党对政治暴力的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/trump-rushed-off-stage-at-pennsylvania-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 22:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
